<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="48100000t" end="73000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">如果是菜月昴大人<br />和爱蜜莉雅大人的话</p>
<p begin="76600000t" end="116100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">想在这里待多久都没问题的…</p>
<p begin="119100000t" end="134000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">谢谢</p>
<p begin="134200000t" end="153900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">但我们还是必须把村子里的人</p>
<p begin="154100000t" end="172400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">给带回去才行</p>
<p begin="176400000t" end="194800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">总之就一次把他们全部带回去</p>
<p begin="195000000t" end="226800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">然后和协力者罗兹瓦尔<br />讨论一下接下来该怎么做吧</p>
<p begin="227000000t" end="239900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">我明白了</p>
<p begin="240200000t" end="281700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">届时如果可以<br />回报你们的恩情就好了</p>
<p begin="281900000t" end="300200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">不用这么夸张啦</p>
<p begin="300500000t" end="320090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">大家都是互相帮助</p>
<p begin="320400000t" end="341500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">而且也拿到报酬啦</p>
<p begin="341700000t" end="357000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">对吧, 帕特拉修</p>
<p begin="380600000t" end="394800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">没事吗, 昴</p>
<p begin="395000000t" end="417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">被鳞片磨比想象中的还要痛啊</p>
<p begin="417200000t" end="445200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">我总算是明白萝卜<br />被磨成泥的感觉了</p>
<p begin="470600000t" end="481600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">昴啾</p>
<p begin="481900000t" end="500800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">我已经把雷姆固定好了</p>
<p begin="501000000t" end="517500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">请务必要保持安静哦</p>
<p begin="539300000t" end="583300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">昴啾也一样<br />回到宅邸后一定要好好静养</p>
<p begin="583500000t" end="592800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">我也?</p>
<p begin="596800000t" end="614000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">你这次和"怠惰"对决的时候</p>
<p begin="614200000t" end="634800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">又过度使用"门"了</p>
<p begin="637500000t" end="667400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">虽然是先暂时把里面的毒素<br />给清干净了</p>
<p begin="667600000t" end="688300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">但应该也要好好休养两个月才行</p>
<p begin="692600000t" end="705300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">两个月吗</p>
<p begin="711600000t" end="745900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">再怎么说应该也不会<br />一直不断遇到事件吧</p>
<p begin="751100000t" end="771400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">等等, 我刚刚是不是立了什么Flag</p>
<p begin="771700000t" end="777900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">好哦</p>
<p begin="778100000t" end="806900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">差不多快到出发的时间了</p>
<p begin="807100000t" end="821100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">那么最后, 请库珥修大人</p>
<p begin="821300000t" end="836400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">对爱蜜莉雅大人他们</p>
<p begin="836600000t" end="848800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">说几句话</p>
<p begin="857000000t" end="868200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="871000000t" end="884400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">愿你平安健康</p>
<p begin="889200000t" end="922500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">期待我们近期内能够再会</p>
<p begin="975000000t" end="986000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">库珥修大人</p>
<p begin="986200000t" end="999100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">请您多多保重</p>
<p begin="1004300000t" end="1035300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">我希望自己不要总是被他人帮助</p>
<p begin="1035500000t" end="1059700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">而是能够成为可以帮助别人的人</p>
<p begin="1088300000t" end="1104200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我也衷心期盼菜月昴大人</p>
<p begin="1104400000t" end="1135100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">未来能够更加活跃</p>
<p begin="1289100000t" end="1316500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">总有一天, 一定会再见的</p>
<p begin="1473600000t" end="1485600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">昴真的是</p>
<p begin="1485900000t" end="1515100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">理所当然的就坐在我旁边了耶</p>
<p begin="1518400000t" end="1540900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">嗯, 有什么奇怪的吗</p>
<p begin="1541100000t" end="1573200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">没有, 一开始虽然觉得有点小介意</p>
<p begin="1578800000t" end="1592400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">但现在如果你没这么做的话</p>
<p begin="1592600000t" end="1610100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我反而会觉得奇怪了呢</p>
<p begin="1619100000t" end="1653100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">看来我艰苦的努力总算是有回报了</p>
<p begin="1653300000t" end="1664500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">太感动了</p>
<p begin="1664800000t" end="1682800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">你又这样敷衍我</p>
<p begin="1693500000t" end="1717200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">你一直很在意雷姆的事情</p>
<p begin="1724000000t" end="1747100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">其实没什么好隐瞒的</p>
<p begin="1765500000t" end="1787900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">她对你来说很重要对吧</p>
<p begin="1788200000t" end="1805500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">重要, 超级重要</p>
<p begin="1805700000t" end="1827500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">和爱蜜莉雅酱一样重要</p>
<p begin="1827800000t" end="1849800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">你有自己说了超自私的话</p>
<p begin="1854700000t" end="1870000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">的自觉吗</p>
<p begin="1870300000t" end="1884300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">有啦</p>
<p begin="1888000000t" end="1913900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">说实话, 丢脸到都想去死了</p>
<p begin="1914200000t" end="1936600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">但是, 我可是非常非常认真的</p>
<p begin="1944700000t" end="1956400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">昴…</p>
<p begin="1983700000t" end="2003400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">刚刚有人叫我吗</p>
<p begin="2003700000t" end="2009700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">什么</p>
<p begin="2014900000t" end="2028200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">没有人叫你啦</p>
<p begin="2031900000t" end="2048300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">话说原来奥托你在啊</p>
<p begin="2048500000t" end="2070700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">当然在啊</p>
<p begin="2071000000t" end="2085500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">不然你以为我到底是为了什么</p>
<p begin="2085700000t" end="2108100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">才帮助昴先生你们的啊</p>
<p begin="2108400000t" end="2122300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">开玩笑的啦</p>
<p begin="2122600000t" end="2151900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">你的目的是和罗兹瓦尔直接交涉嘛</p>
<p begin="2152100000t" end="2163900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">我没有忘记啦</p>
<p begin="2164200000t" end="2176800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">拜托了</p>
<p begin="2177000000t" end="2202500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我可是认真到把人生都赌上了</p>
<p begin="2202700000t" end="2222800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">好啦好啦我知道</p>
<p begin="2223100000t" end="2247000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">接着就是和你暂时说掰掰的时间啦</p>
<p begin="2247200000t" end="2257200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">啊, 等等</p>
<p begin="2334800000t" end="2350400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">一定能找到的</p>
<p begin="2350600000t" end="2372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">把她的"存在"给取回的方法</p>
<p begin="2388300000t" end="2402900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="2403100000t" end="2444400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">而且, 要说因为个人的因素才行动的话</p>
<p begin="2449100000t" end="2477300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">我和昴其实也没什么不同</p>
<p begin="2486600000t" end="2532500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">我也知道自己参加王选的理由<br />其实有些自私</p>
<p begin="2537800000t" end="2549300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">自私?</p>
<p begin="2554300000t" end="2588290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">抱歉, 有点难用言语说明</p>
<p begin="2595700000t" end="2620500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">但我并不是故意要隐瞒你什么</p>
<p begin="2623300000t" end="2644300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">只是不知道怎么说才好…</p>
<p begin="2683000000t" end="2699100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">总之, 和罗兹瓦尔会合以后</p>
<p begin="2699400000t" end="2727600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">再一起好好讨论吧</p>
<p begin="2745200000t" end="2754000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">关于雷姆的问题</p>
<p begin="2754200000t" end="2772500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">说不定他会知道些什么</p>
<p begin="2786800000t" end="2794100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">嗯</p>
<p begin="2812000000t" end="2849100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">两位, 差不多快到目的地咯</p>
<p begin="2894700000t" end="2913400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">没有人在耶</p>
<p begin="2932200000t" end="2947700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">这里也没有人</p>
<p begin="2947900000t" end="2973900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">咦, 为什么</p>
<p begin="2978600000t" end="3006200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">所以拉姆他们还没从"圣域"回来吗</p>
<p begin="3006500000t" end="3021900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">看来是这样没错</p>
<p begin="3026300000t" end="3039600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">对了, 爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="3039900000t" end="3057100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">你知道那个叫"圣域"的地方<br />在哪里吗</p>
<p begin="3060600000t" end="3090900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">咦, 昴你不是知道吗</p>
<p begin="3118300000t" end="3139200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">虽然到这个时候了才问有点那个</p>
<p begin="3139500000t" end="3146800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">不过话说回来</p>
<p begin="3147000000t" end="3167900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">"圣域"到底是什么样的地方啊</p>
<p begin="3168100000t" end="3184100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">我也不太知道</p>
<p begin="3184400000t" end="3214500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">有点像是罗兹瓦尔的<br />秘密基地之类的吧</p>
<p begin="3214700000t" end="3224300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">而且…</p>
<p begin="3224500000t" end="3234200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">而且?</p>
<p begin="3244800000t" end="3260600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">不, 没什么</p>
<p begin="3265400000t" end="3291900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">抱歉, 如果当时有问清楚就好了</p>
<p begin="3292200000t" end="3318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">不不不, 虽说是因为要紧急避难</p>
<p begin="3318800000t" end="3342300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">但也是我太粗心大意了</p>
<p begin="3384200000t" end="3391400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">既然这样的话</p>
<p begin="3391700000t" end="3405700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">总之就先进宅邸吧</p>
<p begin="3409100000t" end="3429000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">说不定会有什么线索</p>
<p begin="3431600000t" end="3451100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">奥托, 你也一起来</p>
<p begin="3453900000t" end="3472200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">咦, 去宅邸吗</p>
<p begin="3472400000t" end="3497100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">都到这里了你还在怕什么啊</p>
<p begin="3497300000t" end="3525200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">龙车和帕特拉修就麻烦你带进去咯</p>
<p begin="3525400000t" end="3541600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">我知道了</p>
<p begin="3593500000t" end="3614000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">我们回来咯, 雷姆</p>
<p begin="3620500000t" end="3630900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">没事吧</p>
<p begin="3646000000t" end="3655100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">话说回来</p>
<p begin="3655300000t" end="3662700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">我有点忘记</p>
<p begin="3663000000t" end="3681200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">离开的时候有没有锁门耶</p>
<p begin="3681400000t" end="3696700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">该不会有小偷跑进去吧</p>
<p begin="3700600000t" end="3733200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">有碧翠丝在应该是不用担心</p>
<p begin="3738200000t" end="3749000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">是不是敲敲门的话</p>
<p begin="3749200000t" end="3768400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">就会出来迎接我们了呢</p>
<p begin="3780800000t" end="3805500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">可能会往帕克飞扑过去哦</p>
<p begin="3808900000t" end="3819000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">是啊</p>
<p begin="3825200000t" end="3844600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">帕克, 帕克</p>
<p begin="3850200000t" end="3874700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">咦, 好像没有反应</p>
<p begin="3875000000t" end="3889000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">是睡着了吗</p>
<p begin="3893200000t" end="3905500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">这边呢</p>
<p begin="3944400000t" end="3965500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">好的, 请稍等一下</p>
<p begin="3965700000t" end="3972400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">咦</p>
<p begin="3984600000t" end="4011300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">爱蜜莉雅大人, 欢迎回来</p>
<p begin="4015400000t" end="4044600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">已久候您多时了</p>
<p begin="4051400000t" end="4063100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="4095100000t" end="4113000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">是的, 是我法兰黛…</p>
<p begin="4113300000t" end="4125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">牙齿好恐怖</p>
<p begin="4143900000t" end="4156800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">请容我重新介绍一次</p>
<p begin="4157000000t" end="4180800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我是以前在这里工作过的</p>
<p begin="4181000000t" end="4199600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">法兰黛莉卡•鲍曼</p>
<p begin="4212900000t" end="4226000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">话说回来</p>
<p begin="4226200000t" end="4243000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">好像是有听说过在我来之前</p>
<p begin="4243300000t" end="4259400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">有女仆刚离开…</p>
<p begin="4259700000t" end="4275500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">因为一些个人因素</p>
<p begin="4275700000t" end="4298400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">稍微休息了一段时间</p>
<p begin="4304100000t" end="4333400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">但是被拉姆叫回来以后</p>
<p begin="4333600000t" end="4350600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">就发现宅邸已经变成空城了</p>
<p begin="4357100000t" end="4383000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">好在从主人大人放在勤务室里的信</p>
<p begin="4383200000t" end="4404100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">总算是了解现在的状况了</p>
<p begin="4406600000t" end="4414600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">信</p>
<p begin="4419400000t" end="4439900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">拉姆叫你回来的理由是什么啊?</p>
<p begin="4447100000t" end="4463500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">我回来的时候</p>
<p begin="4467400000t" end="4493500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">宅邸的厨房还有庭园的植物</p>
<p begin="4493700000t" end="4510600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">都变得很恐怖…</p>
<p begin="4533100000t" end="4551600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">好具体的原因</p>
<p begin="4562700000t" end="4580900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">但是, 真是不可思议耶</p>
<p begin="4581100000t" end="4598200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">法兰黛莉卡不在的时候</p>
<p begin="4598400000t" end="4623000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">应该都是靠拉姆一个人努力完成的啊</p>
<p begin="4626600000t" end="4648100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">为什么才几天时间…</p>
<p begin="4648400000t" end="4657300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">啊</p>
<p begin="4675900000t" end="4688400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">是因为雷姆不在了</p>
<p begin="4688600000t" end="4711000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">拉姆一个人忙不过来</p>
<p begin="4711200000t" end="4733500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">才拜托法兰黛莉卡的吧</p>
<p begin="4748000000t" end="4759700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">可以也跟我说说</p>
<p begin="4759900000t" end="4799200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">这个和拉姆长得一模一样<br />的少女的事吗</p>
<p begin="4804100000t" end="4821200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">她是拉姆的妹妹雷姆</p>
<p begin="4825100000t" end="4842000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">是个很好的孩子</p>
<p begin="4848800000t" end="4864900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">既温柔又强大</p>
<p begin="4865200000t" end="4880600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">工作非常认真</p>
<p begin="4885300000t" end="4895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">从我个人看来</p>
<p begin="4895300000t" end="4924300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">和拉姆的感情真的非常好</p>
<p begin="4935500000t" end="4965000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">一定曾经和你也不错才是</p>
<p begin="4983300000t" end="5012600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">但你应该是…不记得吧</p>
<p begin="5022300000t" end="5035600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">很可惜的</p>
<p begin="5039100000t" end="5058300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">不过不知道主人大人和拉姆</p>
<p begin="5058600000t" end="5078900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">回来以后会是什么反应</p>
<p begin="5084300000t" end="5105500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">虽然不知道罗兹瓦尔的反应会如何</p>
<p begin="5112000000t" end="5143090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">但我真的很不愿意去想象拉姆的反应</p>
<p begin="5155800000t" end="5179090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">法兰黛莉卡, 你有从罗兹瓦尔那里</p>
<p begin="5179290000t" end="5193500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">听说些什么吗</p>
<p begin="5193700000t" end="5213300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">很抱歉, 我不太清楚</p>
<p begin="5213600000t" end="5248300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">主人大人的想法</p>
<p begin="5253400000t" end="5266900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">因为对那位大人来说</p>
<p begin="5267200000t" end="5312800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">这个世界上值得信赖的只有那两位而已</p>
<p begin="5316700000t" end="5324300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">那两位?</p>
<p begin="5327200000t" end="5362300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">就是拉姆和宅邸内<br />禁书库的大精灵大人</p>
<p begin="5366200000t" end="5388100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">禁书库的大精灵?</p>
<p begin="5402800000t" end="5419500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">就是碧翠丝大人哦</p>
<p begin="5532500000t" end="5547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">哦, 碧翠子</p>
<p begin="5547200000t" end="5559100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">好久不见啦</p>
<p begin="5564300000t" end="5603700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">我就在想宅邸怎么这么吵…</p>
<p begin="5624000000t" end="5649800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">大家都很担心你哦</p>
<p begin="5653400000t" end="5661700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">晚一点也没关系</p>
<p begin="5661900000t" end="5677600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">要好好跟大家道歉哦</p>
<p begin="5677800000t" end="5690700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">道歉?</p>
<p begin="5693600000t" end="5703800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">贝蒂吗?</p>
<p begin="5706500000t" end="5716200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">我实在是无法理解</p>
<p begin="5716400000t" end="5744400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">我有什么理由要和谁道歉</p>
<p begin="5744700000t" end="5771100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">那我就去帮你道歉咯</p>
<p begin="5771400000t" end="5783400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">就说你感动落泪到</p>
<p begin="5783600000t" end="5806900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">连鼻水都流一堆出来</p>
<p begin="5807100000t" end="5826700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">不要瞎掰好吗</p>
<p begin="5827000000t" end="5854900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我已经很久没有哭了好不好</p>
<p begin="5855100000t" end="5881400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">偶尔大声的哭一哭也不错哦</p>
<p begin="5881700000t" end="5902700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">不愧是在喜欢的女人膝盖上</p>
<p begin="5902900000t" end="5920800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">哭得唏哩哗啦的男人说出来的话呢</p>
<p begin="5921100000t" end="5936500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">真的是太有道理了</p>
<p begin="5936700000t" end="5964000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">可以拜托你快点忘记那个吗</p>
<p begin="5964200000t" end="5985700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">好了, 差不多该回到主题了吧</p>
<p begin="5986000000t" end="6001400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">你这个胆小鬼</p>
<p begin="6036800000t" end="6058000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">你…对于罗兹瓦尔的想法</p>
<p begin="6058200000t" end="6072500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">大概知道多少</p>
<p begin="6089000000t" end="6119800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">因为有人说<br />如果要问罗兹瓦尔在想些什么的话</p>
<p begin="6120000000t" end="6136100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">找你就对了</p>
<p begin="6141700000t" end="6153300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">谁啊</p>
<p begin="6153600000t" end="6196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">啊, 是那个刚回来的半兽小姑娘啊</p>
<p begin="6202000000t" end="6237600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">确实那个小姑娘的见解还算正确</p>
<p begin="6243000000t" end="6268400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">但是贝蒂和罗兹瓦尔的关系</p>
<p begin="6268700000t" end="6288700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">和这次的事情没有关系</p>
<p begin="6289000000t" end="6317400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">不过你却一个人被留在宅邸里了</p>
<p begin="6321700000t" end="6342400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">在这个什么防护都没做的宅邸里</p>
<p begin="6342700000t" end="6367200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">因为我可以保护自己</p>
<p begin="6367500000t" end="6389100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">所以贝蒂我才留了下来</p>
<p begin="6389400000t" end="6413600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">这点和罗兹瓦尔无关</p>
<p begin="6413800000t" end="6460000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">但是我也不觉得他会什么都不思考</p>
<p begin="6474800000t" end="6500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">所以只是包含你我在内的大家</p>
<p begin="6500500000t" end="6530800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">把罗兹瓦尔想得太厉害了吗</p>
<p begin="6531000000t" end="6561500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">想说面对魔女教不可能毫无对策…</p>
<p begin="6573000000t" end="6582900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">对了</p>
<p begin="6597200000t" end="6608000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">你看看这个</p>
<p begin="6632100000t" end="6650300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">福音书?</p>
<p begin="6650700000t" end="6684700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">为什么偏偏是你拿到那本书啊?</p>
<p begin="6689900000t" end="6710700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">这是我从袭击了宅邸的</p>
<p begin="6710900000t" end="6735800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">魔女教的主谋那里</p>
<p begin="6736000000t" end="6751100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">抢来的战利品</p>
<p begin="6759200000t" end="6777800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">那原本的持有人呢</p>
<p begin="6778100000t" end="6789800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">死掉了</p>
<p begin="6794000000t" end="6812200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">是被我杀死的</p>
<p begin="6839500000t" end="6867900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">你也离我而去了吗</p>
<p begin="6880200000t" end="6890800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">修斯</p>
<p begin="6902300000t" end="6912300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">那是谁</p>
<p begin="6922700000t" end="6937100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">没什么</p>
<p begin="6943100000t" end="6952400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">比起那个</p>
<p begin="6952700000t" end="6971500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">既然你把大罪司教</p>
<p begin="6971700000t" end="6986800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">"怠惰"给杀了的话</p>
<p begin="6987000000t" end="7008300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">那魔女因子变成什么样子了</p>
<p begin="7012800000t" end="7032900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">魔女…因子?</p>
<p begin="7037500000t" end="7047300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">你不知道吗</p>
<p begin="7047600000t" end="7063600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">真的还假的啊</p>
<p begin="7070100000t" end="7076400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">既然如此</p>
<p begin="7076700000t" end="7107500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">你是为了什么才把<br />"怠惰"给杀掉的啊</p>
<p begin="7111000000t" end="7131200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">还有罗兹瓦尔到底在做什么</p>
<p begin="7131500000t" end="7168400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">我刚刚就说了<br />罗兹瓦尔那家伙在"圣域"啊</p>
<p begin="7168600000t" end="7194700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">所以才想知道他到底在想些什么</p>
<p begin="7214900000t" end="7240100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">你要的答案</p>
<p begin="7240300000t" end="7261200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">应该都在那个"圣域"里面吧</p>
<p begin="7266600000t" end="7274400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">什么</p>
<p begin="7274700000t" end="7293400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">罗兹瓦尔的想法</p>
<p begin="7293600000t" end="7307600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">福音书的意义</p>
<p begin="7307800000t" end="7322900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">还有魔女因子的答案</p>
<p begin="7323200000t" end="7342200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">应该全部都在那里吧</p>
<p begin="7349200000t" end="7365600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">想知道的话就去吧</p>
<p begin="7374700000t" end="7405000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">地点的话半兽的小姑娘会告诉你的</p>
<p begin="7409900000t" end="7419200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">等等</p>
<p begin="7419400000t" end="7434000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">怎么突然…</p>
<p begin="7434200000t" end="7452900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">为什么突然就愿意说了</p>
<p begin="7453100000t" end="7469600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">而且就算不去"圣域"</p>
<p begin="7469900000t" end="7473700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">你也…</p>
<p begin="7473900000t" end="7489900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我不会说的</p>
<p begin="7496100000t" end="7523500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">我应该也有不说的权利吧</p>
<p begin="7543900000t" end="7566000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">我已经告诉你通往答案的道路了</p>
<p begin="7569500000t" end="7595400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">你能不能不要再跟贝蒂撒娇了</p>
<p begin="7595700000t" end="7603100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">碧翠子</p>
<p begin="7603400000t" end="7614300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="7614500000t" end="7650100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">我可不是你便利的道具啊</p>
<p begin="7697700000t" end="7731500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">为什么菜月先生<br />会从我刚刚上完厕所的地方跑出来啊</p>
<p begin="7731800000t" end="7773100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">为什么你又一副快哭出来的样子啊</p>
<p begin="7773300000t" end="7790900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">那个, 可以请你快点让开吗</p>
<p begin="7814900000t" end="7852500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">碧翠丝大人真的还待在禁书库里面吗</p>
<p begin="7852800000t" end="7863500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">怎么了</p>
<p begin="7863800000t" end="7877200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">你怀疑我吗</p>
<p begin="7877400000t" end="7884700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">是的</p>
<p begin="7885000000t" end="7903300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">但是刚刚爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="7903500000t" end="7926300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">已经和我说了自己到底</p>
<p begin="7926600000t" end="7953700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">有多依靠菜月昴大人了</p>
<p begin="7959700000t" end="7985100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">所以我就抱着一点期待等着了</p>
<p begin="7992100000t" end="8004800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">等等, 法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="8005100000t" end="8026300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">什么, 你们说了些什么</p>
<p begin="8026500000t" end="8036400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">不是的</p>
<p begin="8036600000t" end="8063800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">我的确是和法兰黛莉卡<br />说了关于昴的事情</p>
<p begin="8067300000t" end="8079100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">但也没那么夸张…</p>
<p begin="8079300000t" end="8106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">不, 我当时也在一旁听着</p>
<p begin="8106300000t" end="8134100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">真的是不能小看菜月先生呢</p>
<p begin="8134300000t" end="8148300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">连奥托也?</p>
<p begin="8148600000t" end="8184500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">为什么我不在现场啦<br />这样不就没听到吗</p>
<p begin="8184700000t" end="8207400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">昴在场的话我说不出口啦</p>
<p begin="8211200000t" end="8223400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">够了啦, 法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="8223600000t" end="8236500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">请继续说下去</p>
<p begin="8236800000t" end="8247500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">好好好</p>
<p begin="8247700000t" end="8259900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">我知道了</p>
<p begin="8265300000t" end="8294300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">那么为了让事情能够进展下去</p>
<p begin="8294500000t" end="8305500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">我们来讨论一下吧</p>
<p begin="8305700000t" end="8318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">能够进展下去</p>
<p begin="8318800000t" end="8328200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">那是什么意思</p>
<p begin="8328500000t" end="8347800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">就算昴见到了碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="8348000000t" end="8377000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">但那孩子会不会回答问题又是另一回事了</p>
<p begin="8379700000t" end="8416700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">因为昴和碧翠丝都很固执嘛</p>
<p begin="8421800000t" end="8447300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">虽然很在意你表达的太可爱了这件事</p>
<p begin="8447600000t" end="8455900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">但的确是这样</p>
<p begin="8459200000t" end="8467700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">然后呢</p>
<p begin="8472100000t" end="8503000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">因为我也有很多想和罗兹瓦尔说的话</p>
<p begin="8508200000t" end="8529400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">所以就拜托法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="8529600000t" end="8548700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">告诉我"圣域"的所在地</p>
<p begin="8562200000t" end="8594800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">地点的话半兽的小姑娘会告诉你的</p>
<p begin="8602800000t" end="8628400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">法兰黛莉卡会告诉我们吗</p>
<p begin="8628600000t" end="8656900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">虽然有被提醒过尽量不要说出去</p>
<p begin="8657200000t" end="8694900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">但我没办法拒绝爱蜜莉雅大人啊</p>
<p begin="8699400000t" end="8731600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">不过, 需要一些准备的时间</p>
<p begin="8738400000t" end="8754900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">大约两天左右吧</p>
<p begin="8755100000t" end="8768000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">准备是指?</p>
<p begin="8772200000t" end="8787100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">是这样啊</p>
<p begin="8787400000t" end="8806400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">大家会有几天都不在宅邸</p>
<p begin="8806600000t" end="8814500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">所以要准备一下</p>
<p begin="8814700000t" end="8841700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">不, 我会留在这里</p>
<p begin="8842000000t" end="8857600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">不会和您一起同行</p>
<p begin="8857900000t" end="8876400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">你不一起去吗</p>
<p begin="8876700000t" end="8893000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">那我们要怎么去呢</p>
<p begin="8918500000t" end="8942900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">你也太迟钝了吧, 菜月先生</p>
<p begin="8966000000t" end="9004400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">啊, 所以是奥托要跟我们去"圣域"</p>
<p begin="9009300000t" end="9033800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">借由通过帮助爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="9034100000t" end="9055900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">来提升在做为协力者的<br />罗兹瓦尔心中的印象吗</p>
<p begin="9056100000t" end="9071200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">不是, 那个…</p>
<p begin="9074900000t" end="9097100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">奥托君, 是这样吗</p>
<p begin="9097400000t" end="9116500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">爱蜜莉雅大人用如此纯真的眼神</p>
<p begin="9116700000t" end="9126700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">看得我好痛啊</p>
<p begin="9126900000t" end="9146700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">对不起, 就是如此</p>
<p begin="9146900000t" end="9164600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">你总是很容易暴露自己的企图</p>
<p begin="9164800000t" end="9177200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">这让我对你的好感度特别高哦</p>
<p begin="9177500000t" end="9185200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">奥托</p>
<p begin="9185500000t" end="9199200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">被菜月先生这么说</p>
<p begin="9199500000t" end="9216500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">让我有点无法释怀啊</p>
<p begin="9216700000t" end="9231200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">总之你要来帮忙我了解了</p>
<p begin="9236400000t" end="9268600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">所以, 就跟我们3个人说说<br />关于"圣域"的事情吧</p>
<p begin="9276700000t" end="9291000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">我知道了</p>
<p begin="9302900000t" end="9322700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">接下来要说的是</p>
<p begin="9323000000t" end="9335700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">千万不可以对外说出去的</p>
<p begin="9335900000t" end="9363300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">前往"克雷马尔堤的圣域"的方法</p>
<p begin="9369400000t" end="9376400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">还有</p>
<p begin="9376600000t" end="9417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">到"圣域"时请务必要小心并记住</p>
<p begin="9420700000t" end="9453600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">一个名叫加菲尔的人</p>
<p begin="9458800000t" end="9473600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">这个人也是在"圣域"当中</p>
<p begin="9473800000t" end="9532400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">爱蜜莉雅大人你们最需要小心因应的人</p>
<p begin="9600900000t" end="9627800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">雷姆, 我走咯</p>
<p begin="9634100000t" end="9666500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">法兰黛莉卡会好好照顾你的</p>
<p begin="9666800000t" end="9684600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">要乖乖等我们哦</p>
<p begin="9785700000t" end="9798300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">好了吗</p>
<p begin="9798500000t" end="9813200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">哦, 新来的</p>
<p begin="9813400000t" end="9833800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">有好好地穿着制服呢</p>
<p begin="9837300000t" end="9850100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">是吧</p>
<p begin="9870300000t" end="9895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">已经好好跟雷姆小姐道别了吗</p>
<p begin="9899400000t" end="9916900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">大概就那样吧</p>
<p begin="9921200000t" end="9943300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">虽然不想在那边待太久</p>
<p begin="9943500000t" end="9959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">但就是想来看看</p>
<p begin="9967800000t" end="9981200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">我不在的时候</p>
<p begin="9981500000t" end="10007700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">可以请你好好照顾雷姆吗</p>
<p begin="10008000000t" end="10015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">佩特拉</p>
<p begin="10020500000t" end="10029800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">我知道了</p>
<p begin="10030000000t" end="10040600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">昴大人</p>
<p begin="10049500000t" end="10077400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">不过, 应征女仆也才两天</p>
<p begin="10080700000t" end="10103700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">到宅邸报到实际上也才一天</p>
<p begin="10104000000t" end="10128200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">真亏你能顺利地找到我呢</p>
<p begin="10132600000t" end="10157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">这个年纪就决定离开父母</p>
<p begin="10157300000t" end="10170100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">真是太了不起了</p>
<p begin="10170400000t" end="10185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">我已经12岁了</p>
<p begin="10185600000t" end="10204800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">是可以好好工作的大人了呢</p>
<p begin="10205100000t" end="10224100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">不对, 是"已经是大人了"</p>
<p begin="10227000000t" end="10259500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">所以也请昴大人<br />好好地把我当作大人对待</p>
<p begin="10259700000t" end="10276600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">等你变成敬语大师</p>
<p begin="10276800000t" end="10295690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">能通过法兰黛莉卡那关的话</p>
<p begin="10295890000t" end="10307200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">我会的哦</p>
<p begin="10307500000t" end="10314800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">嗯</p>
<p begin="10315100000t" end="10330500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">啊不对, 是!</p>
<p begin="10386400000t" end="10399900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">认真想躲起来的话</p>
<p begin="10400100000t" end="10419400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">还真的是满难找的</p>
<p begin="10423800000t" end="10449700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">真的有那么不可思议的房间吗</p>
<p begin="10450000000t" end="10468290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">啊, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="10468590000t" end="10483690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">佩特拉也知道的吧</p>
<p begin="10487400000t" end="10506300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">也注意一下那家伙比较好</p>
<p begin="10512400000t" end="10555000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">有时候打开门就会随机遇到也说不定</p>
<p begin="10555200000t" end="10567900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">等等, 昴大人</p>
<p begin="10568100000t" end="10588500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">你对我的要求好像也太多了吧</p>
<p begin="10592900000t" end="10608200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">我知道, 抱歉</p>
<p begin="10612900000t" end="10631600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">但是也只能拜托你了</p>
<p begin="10631800000t" end="10646700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">真的很对不起</p>
<p begin="10679800000t" end="10693800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">真是没办法啊</p>
<p begin="10694000000t" end="10718500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">你都这样说了就交给我吧</p>
<p begin="10718800000t" end="10738200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">嗯, 真的帮大忙了</p>
<p begin="10753700000t" end="10773700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">宅邸的事就麻烦你了</p>
<p begin="10773900000t" end="10802800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">还有雷姆, 佩特拉, 碧翠丝也是</p>
<p begin="10806500000t" end="10821500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">请交给我吧</p>
<p begin="10821700000t" end="10851000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">爱蜜莉雅大人也请您路上小心</p>
<p begin="10859000000t" end="10874300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">还有, 这个…</p>
<p begin="10881900000t" end="10891800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">有这个的话</p>
<p begin="10892000000t" end="10906700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">就可以穿过森林的结界</p>
<p begin="10906900000t" end="10927600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">进入"圣域"了</p>
<p begin="10934300000t" end="10957600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">接着只要照我跟您说的走</p>
<p begin="10957800000t" end="10978200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">地龙就会带您们到那里的</p>
<p begin="10983000000t" end="11018700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">这颗石头就是通过结界的条件吗</p>
<p begin="11057500000t" end="11077800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">"地点"和"资格"已经齐全了</p>
<p begin="11084000000t" end="11109800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">接着就是觉悟和强大的意志了…</p>
<p begin="11126900000t" end="11137500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="11173300000t" end="11196700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">就麻烦您们前往"圣域"了</p>
<p begin="11200400000t" end="11228100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">还有, 请别忘了我告诉过您们的话</p>
<p begin="11241000000t" end="11270200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">绝对要小心加菲尔对吧</p>
<p begin="11279200000t" end="11286700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">那个</p>
<p begin="11286900000t" end="11298300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">昴大人</p>
<p begin="11306100000t" end="11329600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">可以请您收下这个吗</p>
<p begin="11332700000t" end="11342700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">那个…</p>
<p begin="11342900000t" end="11369600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">送行的时候递上白手帕</p>
<p begin="11369900000t" end="11384900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">希望对方能在旅行的途中不要弄脏</p>
<p begin="11385200000t" end="11400800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">并好好地归还</p>
<p begin="11408000000t" end="11439200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">以前开始就是一种<br />期许对方旅途平安的传统</p>
<p begin="11442500000t" end="11460600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">是这样的东西啊</p>
<p begin="11467900000t" end="11475500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">我知道了</p>
<p begin="11475800000t" end="11488700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">谢谢你, 佩特拉</p>
<p begin="11494200000t" end="11507100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">我一定会还给你的</p>
<p begin="11577900000t" end="11585100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">咦</p>
<p begin="11585300000t" end="11603200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">为什么那个反应</p>
<p begin="11609500000t" end="11625500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">突然进入叛逆期了吗</p>
<p begin="11625700000t" end="11638500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">我好寂寞啊</p>
<p begin="11656600000t" end="11675600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">好了, 请快点出发吧</p>
<p begin="11681800000t" end="11700000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">克雷马尔堤圣域的迷路森林</p>
<p begin="11700300000t" end="11728500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">越晚会变得越危险哦</p>
<p begin="11759500000t" end="11781000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">祝福你们一路平安</p>
<p begin="11793000000t" end="11820100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">昴大人</p>
<p begin="11820400000t" end="11856200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">要好好保护大姐姐哦</p>
<p begin="11869700000t" end="11899800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">这样就完成主人大人嘱咐的…</p>
<p begin="11913800000t" end="11941800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">接着除了祈祷爱蜜莉雅大人他们能</p>
<p begin="11942100000t" end="11962800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">平安的通过"圣域"以外</p>
<p begin="11970500000t" end="11991100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">也没什么能做的了</p>
<p begin="12017600000t" end="12036700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">帕克那家伙一直都没出来露脸吗</p>
<p begin="12042200000t" end="12051800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">是啊</p>
<p begin="12052000000t" end="12068800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">已经叫了好几次</p>
<p begin="12069100000t" end="12093000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">而且契约的连结也都还感觉的到</p>
<p begin="12099100000t" end="12119400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">以前有发生过类似的事吗</p>
<p begin="12119700000t" end="12141100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">虽然是没有像这样的事</p>
<p begin="12141400000t" end="12157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">但的确是有发生过好几次</p>
<p begin="12157200000t" end="12179700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">连续几天都找不到人的情形</p>
<p begin="12203400000t" end="12235100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">莉雅就拜托你了哦</p>
<p begin="12239900000t" end="12248300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">该不会…</p>
<p begin="12260400000t" end="12283500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">不过, 我也有和微精灵的孩子们</p>
<p begin="12283700000t" end="12295300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">签过契约</p>
<p begin="12295600000t" end="12316300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">这些孩子们也能战斗</p>
<p begin="12316500000t" end="12325700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">发生什么的话</p>
<p begin="12326000000t" end="12340100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">也能保护昴</p>
<p begin="12343400000t" end="12359700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">讨厌, 超man的</p>
<p begin="12361600000t" end="12370700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">真是的</p>
<p begin="12388200000t" end="12401500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">说不定会发生什么</p>
<p begin="12401800000t" end="12430600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">说的是法兰黛莉卡的忠告吧</p>
<p begin="12441700000t" end="12457400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">加菲尔对吧</p>
<p begin="12457600000t" end="12477500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">嗯, 罗兹瓦尔好像也说过</p>
<p begin="12477800000t" end="12504400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">曾经去找过那家伙几次</p>
<p begin="12504700000t" end="12513700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">那个</p>
<p begin="12518900000t" end="12534600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">进入森林了</p>
<p begin="12574800000t" end="12594200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">克雷马尔堤的迷路森林</p>
<p begin="12598200000t" end="12635700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">其中的"圣域"被特殊的结界给守护</p>
<p begin="12640200000t" end="12659300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">会远离外人</p>
<p begin="12659600000t" end="12676600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">并误导路径</p>
<p begin="12676900000t" end="12708000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">所以被称为迷路森林</p>
<p begin="12716500000t" end="12742000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">"圣域"就在这前方吗</p>
<p begin="12806900000t" end="12817400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="12817700000t" end="12837200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">难不成你在紧张吗</p>
<p begin="12846400000t" end="12861700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">你怎么知道的</p>
<p begin="12861900000t" end="12885300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">只要是你的事我都知道</p>
<p begin="12885500000t" end="12901200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">虽然是很想这么说</p>
<p begin="12901400000t" end="12920800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">但以你刚刚的样子任谁都看得出来啦</p>
<p begin="12965000000t" end="12978600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">真的耶</p>
<p begin="12993600000t" end="13012100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">抱歉让你担心了</p>
<p begin="13016500000t" end="13033300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">一想到马上就要到"圣域"</p>
<p begin="13033500000t" end="13060200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">只有亚人族的村庄时…</p>
<p begin="13066100000t" end="13079800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">我才不好意思</p>
<p begin="13080100000t" end="13101900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">没有顾虑到那么多</p>
<p begin="13109000000t" end="13122100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">说不定会有和爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="13122300000t" end="13149700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">一样遭遇的半妖精也说不定</p>
<p begin="13154800000t" end="13192000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">我从没见过自己以外的半妖精</p>
<p begin="13199200000t" end="13225200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">但是在"圣域"的话说不定…</p>
<p begin="13232900000t" end="13244900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">没事的</p>
<p begin="13248800000t" end="13256700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">我会</p>
<p begin="13276500000t" end="13288000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="13293900000t" end="13310800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">咦, 这是</p>
<p begin="13311000000t" end="13332900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">我有很不好的预感</p>
<p begin="13333100000t" end="13346100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">爱蜜莉雅借我一下</p>
<p begin="13387800000t" end="13397000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="13516800000t" end="13537800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499">这里是哪里啊</p>
<p begin="13627600000t" end="13640500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500">你是</p>
<p begin="13653600000t" end="13666200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501">那个耳朵</p>
<p begin="13666400000t" end="13681500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502">该不会是妖精</p>
<p begin="13694500000t" end="13703600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503">等等</p>
<p begin="13703800000t" end="13716700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504">等等我啊</p>
<p begin="13818900000t" end="13829400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505">喂</p>
<p begin="13833800000t" end="13849200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506">有人在吗</p>
<p begin="13855500000t" end="13871100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507">如果这里是"圣域"的话</p>
<p begin="13871300000t" end="13889600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508">就给我点回应吧</p>
<p begin="13931100000t" end="13944300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509">这是…</p>
<p begin="14093300000t" end="14104000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510">原来如此</p>
<p begin="14111200000t" end="14137200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511">那就是你欲望的根源吗</p>
<p begin="14137400000t" end="14160200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512">还真是有趣呢</p>
<p begin="14258200000t" end="14286000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513">哎呀, 吓到你了吗</p>
<p begin="14321900000t" end="14352600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514">因为太久没和人类说话</p>
<p begin="14352900000t" end="14376700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515">所以情绪比较高昂</p>
<p begin="14389000000t" end="14411200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516">我的名字是艾姬多娜</p>
<p begin="14416300000t" end="14432700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517">还是你应该称呼我为</p>
<p begin="14433000000t" end="14462200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518">"强欲的魔女"比较好呢</p>
<p begin="14470300000t" end="14499200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519">(下一个地方)</p>
</div>
